data.description: Discover the perfect blend of elegance and nature in this 3-bed, 2-bath home. Enjoy breathtaking mountain views from your expansive three-quarter acre lot. The community offers a refreshing swimming pool, small intimate clubhouse and tennis courts, ensuring both relaxation and recreation at your doorstep. Your idyllic lifestyle starts here. Updated bathroom, new water heater in 2020,New Roof ($40,000) installed 11/24/2023, and has an extra room added for additional living space.Comes with a Choice home warranty plan!
